Developer Terms of Use
des:
Old MacDonald Had A Farm provides an interactive version of the favorite childhood song. You pick the animals that Old MacDonald had on his farm, and sing along with each verse.
Animals include favorites such as the cow, pig, horse, duck, dog as well as others. For times when you do not want the interactivity, the skill can choose random animals.
